    "actor_description": "I trip over my own timing—words landing half a beat off, hands suddenly unsure where to go. Heat crawls up my neck as my attention snaps tight, replaying the last second like I can fix it by staring harder. I try to smooth it out, but the harder I push, the more aware I am of pushing. Then I force a tiny reset: breathe, soften, move on.",
